fields.name: Develop mobile app prototype
fields.description:
Conduct Requirements Analysis: Review the project requirements, user stories, and any provided design specifications or wireframes. Gain a clear understanding of the target audience, app functionality, and desired user flow.

 Identify Key Features: Determine the core features and functionalities that need to be included in the prototype. This may include user registration, login, navigation, data input, data retrieval, and other relevant features.
Sketch Initial Wireframes: Create rough sketches or wireframes to visualize the app's layout, structure, and basic navigation. Focus on capturing the main screens and user interactions to convey the intended flow of the app.

Design UI Elements: Develop a consistent and visually appealing user interface design.
